      <title>ING 报告成本高于预期，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ing-raises-its-revenue-outlook-as-profit-beats-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰银行 ING Groep NV 股价下跌，因为其报告的成本高于预期，且一项关键的财务实力指标低于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ing-raises-its-revenue-outlook-as-profit-beats-estimates</guid>
